'''藍迪·亞羅薩倫納'''（{{lang-en|Randy Arozarena}}，{{bd|1995年|2月28日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的外野手，目前效力於坦帕灣光芒。他生涯曾效力過紅雀隊。2020年10月28日，他在季後賽敲出10支全壘打，為大聯盟在季後賽敲出最多轟的菜鳥球員。

==職業生涯==
===聖路易紅雀===
2016年7月，亞羅薩倫納與紅雀隊簽約。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cbssports.com/fantasy/baseball/news/cardinals-randy-arozarena-signs-with-cardinals-for-125-million/amp|title=Cardinals' Randy Arozarena: Signs with Cardinals for $1.25 million|date=July 27, 2016|agency=RotoWire Staff|publisher=[[CBS_Sports|CBS Sports]]|work=cbssports.com|accessdate=February 24, 2018|archive-date=2020-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017041504/https://www.cbssports.com/fantasy/baseball/news/cardinals-randy-arozarena-signs-with-cardinals-for-125-million/amp/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2018年7月，他入選了未來之星明星賽。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cardinal-beat/minor-league-report-hudson-arozarena-tabbed-for-all-star-futures/article_cbbde2b3-b032-5fa4-85f2-65eac06d2cb4.html|title=Minor league report: Hudson, Arozarena tabbed for All-Star Futures Game|date=July 6, 2018|last=Baugh|first=Peter|publisher=[[St._Louis_Post-Dispatch|St. Louis Post-Dispatch]]|work=stltoday.com|accessdate=July 9, 2018|archive-date=2021-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210509221213/https://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cardinal-beat/minor-league-report-hudson-arozarena-tabbed-for-all-star-futures/article_cbbde2b3-b032-5fa4-85f2-65eac06d2cb4.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年8月14日，亞羅薩倫納升上大聯盟。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cardinal-beat/here-comes-arozarena-as-cardinals-place-j-martinez-on-il/article_6fb92b71-276e-5f57-9abf-77c001e7967d.html|title=Here comes Arozarena as Cardinals place J. Martinez on IL|date=August 12, 2019|last=Hummel|first=Rick|publisher=[[St._Louis_Post-Dispatch|St. Louis Post-Dispatch]]|work=stltoday.com|accessdate=August 12, 2019|archive-date=2021-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210509221215/https://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cardinal-beat/here-comes-arozarena-as-cardinals-place-j-martinez-on-il/article_6fb92b71-276e-5f57-9abf-77c001e7967d.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/cardinals/news/cardinals-sweep-rival-royals-with-two-shutouts|title=Cards break up no-hit bid, sweep Royals|date=August 14, 2019|last=Brown|first=David|publisher=Major League Baseball|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|accessdate=August 15, 2019|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028204832/https://www.mlb.com/cardinals/news/cardinals-sweep-rival-royals-with-two-shutouts|dead-url=no}}</ref>該年他出賽19場比賽，打擊率為3成，並敲出1轟、2分打點與2次盜壘成功。
===坦帕灣光芒===
2020年1月9日，亞羅薩倫納和José Martínez一同被交易至光芒隊，紅雀隊得到Matthew Liberatore和Edgardo Rodriguez。<ref>{{cite web|title=Cardinals send Jose Martinez, Randy Arozarena to Rays for pitching prospect Matthew Liberatore|url=https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/cardinals-send-jose-martinez-randy-arozarena-to-rays-for-pitching-prospect-matthew-liberatore|date=January 9, 2020|last=Anderson|first=R.J.|publisher=[[CBS_Sports|CBS Sports]]|work=cbssports.com|accessdate=June 13, 2020|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226043704/https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/cardinals-send-jose-martinez-randy-arozarena-to-rays-for-pitching-prospect-matthew-liberatore/|dead-url=no}}</ref>該年他出賽23場比賽，打擊率為2成81，並敲出7轟與11分打點。他在美聯冠軍賽第七戰敲出2分砲，這是他季後賽的第7轟。打破了2008年由[[埃文·朗歌利亞|埃文·朗歌利亞]]創下的菜鳥球員在季後賽保持的6轟紀錄。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://en.liderendeportes.com/news/baseball/arozarena-breaks-home-run-mark-for-a-rookie/|access-date=2020-10-19|website=en.liderendeportes.com|title=存档副本|archive-date=2020-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019083120/https://en.liderendeportes.com/news/baseball/arozarena-breaks-home-run-mark-for-a-rookie/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

他在系列賽繳出打擊率3成21，外帶4轟與6分打點的成績。順勢拿下美聯冠軍賽的MVP。

[[2020年世界大賽|2020年世界大賽]]第四戰，亞羅薩倫納於4局下開轟，成為大聯盟於單一季後賽敲出最多全壘打的選手（9轟）。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://tw.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%B7-%E5%85%89%E8%8A%92%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%80%E5%86%8D%E9%96%8B%E8%BD%9F-%E5%88%B7%E6%96%B0%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-024130973.html |title=光芒新秀再開轟！刷新聯盟紀錄 |access-date=2020-10-25 |archive-date=2020-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028211545/https://tw.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%B7-%E5%85%89%E8%8A%92%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%80%E5%86%8D%E9%96%8B%E8%BD%9F-%E5%88%B7%E6%96%B0%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-024130973.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==個人生活==
亞羅薩倫納的女兒在2018年出生於墨西哥。他的弟弟Raiko是一名足球員，目前在墨西哥足球協會打球。<ref>{{cite web|title='He stands out': Arozarena's star on the rise|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/randy-arozarena-could-be-rays-star-in-the-making|date=October 2, 2020|last=Toribio|first=Juan|publisher=Major League Baseball|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|accessdate=October 2, 2020|archive-date=2020-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230040724/https://www.mlb.com/news/randy-arozarena-could-be-rays-star-in-the-making|dead-url=no}}</ref>
